## Typography Enforcement

### Type Scale (Must Use)

| Purpose             | Class pattern                                                                      |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Page titles         | `text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl`                               |
| Section headers     | `text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight`                                            |
| Card titles         | `text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight` or `text-sm font-semibold` (compact cards) |
| Subsection headers  | `text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight`                                             |
| Body text           | `text-sm` (14px -- this is the default)                                            |
| Secondary text      | `text-xs text-muted-foreground`                                                    |
| Captions            | `text-[10px] text-muted-foreground`                                                |
| Form section titles | `text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider`               |

### FORBIDDEN Typography

- `text-base` as default body (our body is `text-sm`)
- `text-lg` without semantic purpose
- Arbitrary font sizes like `text-[15px]`
- Missing `tracking-tight` on headers
- Using `font-bold` instead of `font-semibold` on headers (except h1)

---

## Spacing Grid Enforcement

### 4px Base Grid

All spacing must align to the 4px grid:

| Allowed values | Tailwind              |
| -------------- | --------------------- |
| 4px            | `p-1`, `m-1`, `gap-1` |
| 8px            | `p-2`, `m-2`, `gap-2` |
| 12px           | `p-3`, `m-3`, `gap-3` |
| 16px           | `p-4`, `m-4`, `gap-4` |
| 20px           | `p-5`, `m-5`, `gap-5` |
| 24px           | `p-6`, `m-6`, `gap-6` |
| 32px           | `p-8`, `m-8`, `gap-8` |

### FORBIDDEN Spacing

- Arbitrary values: `p-[13px]`, `m-[7px]`, `gap-[5px]`
- Zero values where spacing is expected (unless intentional like `pt-0` on CardContent)
- Mixing spacing scales (e.g., `gap-3` and `gap-5` on sibling containers)

### Component Spacing Patterns

| Component           | Required spacing           |
| ------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Card padding        | `p-6` (24px)               |
| CardHeader          | `space-y-1.5` internal     |
| CardContent         | `p-6 pt-0`                 |
| Section spacing     | `space-y-4` to `space-y-8` |
| Form label to input | `space-y-2`                |
| Button group gap    | `gap-2`                    |
| Icon to text        | `gap-2`                    |

