## Component Anatomy Patterns

### Card

```
<Card>                           /* border bg-card shadow-sm rounded-lg */
  <CardHeader className="pb-2">  /* tight bottom when content follows */
    <CardTitle>                   /* text-sm font-semibold (compact) */
    <CardDescription>             /* text-xs text-muted-foreground */
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent className="pt-0"> /* zero top when header above */
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

### Form Section

```
<section className="space-y-4">
  <h2 className="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider">
  /* form fields with space-y-2 */
</section>
```

### Badge Variants

```
<Badge variant="outline" className="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200">
<Badge variant="outline" className="bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border-amber-200">
<Badge variant="outline" className="bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 border-rose-200">
```

---

## Required Patterns on Every Interactive Element

1. **Focus ring**: `focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring`
2. **Transition**: `transition-colors` for color changes, `transition-transform` for movement
3. **Disabled state**: `disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50`
4. **Cursor**: Buttons and clickable elements use `cursor-pointer` (set globally for non-disabled buttons)

---

## Class Merging

Always use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` to merge Tailwind classes. Never concatenate class strings manually:

```
// Correct
className={cn("base-classes", conditional && "conditional-classes", className)}

// Wrong
className={`base-classes ${conditional ? 'conditional-classes' : ''}`}
```

